         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. &amp; zoolog. Garden ¶ 12 April 1861. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ Referring to your minute, dated 7/2.61, ¶ M to J. Moore, 4 February 1861, n. 3. ¶  ¶ according to which you desired to entrust the supervisi...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">61.04.12a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To John Moore</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">R61/2751, unit 749, VPRS 1189/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS written by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Carl Wilhelmi</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and signed by M. See also M to J. Moore, 4 February 1861.</p>
               </note>Melbourne bot. &amp; zoolog. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">12 April 1861.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Referring to your minute, dated 7/2.61,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M to J. Moore, 4 February 1861, n. 3.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>according to which you desired to entrust the supervision of the six Dromedaries to the zoological Committee and requested me to provide for the future care of the animals, I have the honor to report, that they have hitherto remained under the attendance of the Hindostan "Esau", who is evidently a trustworthy man, well acquainted with their requirements. The Bailiff Scott of Royal Park is moreover daily superintending the management of the Dromedaries.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Rations according to the schedule approved of by the Hon. the Chief Secretary are monthly issued, unless surplus rations remain available, and will according to the decision of the Hon. Chief Secretary be charged to the Exploration Vote, and of which also the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>maintainance<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>remuneration<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of the Lascar, I anticipate, is to be provided.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As the liquidation of wages and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>maintainance<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>expenses for the Indian is due since some time, as well as the settlement of some smaller incidental accounts for articles required and supplied for the Dromedaries, I have the honor to solicit, that the hon. the Chief Secretary will be pleased to issue the authority to defray these pendent and fulture<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>future?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>expenses connected with the sustenance of the Camels and their Keeper.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg to add, that the animals are now in good health and condition and are supplied at present also with Mangold wurzel<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Common beet.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from the Experimental farm.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In the requisition annexed<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Annexed document<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I beg to provide for the supply of some articles, which are urgently needed for the keeping of the Dromedaries, and the use of their attendant.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Moore minuted approval for M's requisition on 16 April 1861 and told him the requisition had been forwarded to the Government Storekeeper: 'Dr Mueller can submit any accounts due for the maintenance of the camels. He will oblige by returning as soon as<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>possible this paper and those marked 791 999'. M replied<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in a further minute<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on 17 April: 'Papers returned as desired &amp; thanks hereby expressed for information'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Mr Undersecretary Moore</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
